body.description: Our latest innovation in the baby diaper and pull-up sector is designed to provide customers with the highest quality standards at the best prices. Introducing our eco-friendly baby diapers and pull-ups, thoughtfully crafted for comfort, leak protection, and environmental sustainability. These products are hypoallergenic, free of harmful chemicals, and made from natural fibers to prevent rashes and allergies. With impressive absorbency and durability, they offer all-day protection. What makes them stand out is their high-quality build and their eco-friendliness, as they are up to 80% biodegradable, minimizing your environmental footprint. Choose our products for a greener future without compromising on your baby's well-being. Absorbent core: One fluff pad (from Weyerhaeuser) made of 100% long fibers, chlorine-free cellulose. One absorbency paper makes the absorb faster and surface dryer. Super absorbent: Sodium polyacrylate, non-allergenic. Highly absorbent and restrained odors. Acquisition Layer: Third layer to keep the skin dry (100% propylene, very soft touch). Cover stock: 100% polypropylene, softness non-woven non-allergenic, for sanitary use. Pearl design with a super soft touch. Leak guard: Special raised leak guard to avoid long-term leaks. 100% polypropylene, hydrophobic 3D design gives more comfort. Back sheet: Triple textile back sheet breathable. The first layer with hydrophilic 100% polypropylene. Second layer: non-toxic polyethylene for impermeability. Third layer: 100% polypropylene for softness touch and breathable. Wetness indicator: Triple wetness for better security. The wetness indicator will change color when it’s wet. Glue: Hot melt adhesive; non-toxic. Elastics: 2 very tight elastic threads to keep raised leak guard, 3 siding elastics for leg cuff (latex free). Min tape: Two big mini soft tapes. Waistband: Big waistband gives babies more comfort and move freely
